        {
            "title": "中國將曝出華為晶片秘密研究公司列入黑名單",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"中國將曝出華為晶片秘密研究公司列入黑名單\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Xo.LMV.YcF4qopA8T_PLbQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/6eb26fe0-a506-11f0-bea7-9f44e995625d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國將曝出華為晶片秘密研究公司列入黑名單</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
