        {
            "title": "避險需求遇上緊俏市場 現貨白銀創出數十年新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 現貨白銀價格飆升至數十年來的最高水平，因投資者加大轉向貴金屬尋求避險的同時市場趨於緊俏。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">銀價周四一度上漲1.9%，觸及每盎司49.824美元，創下彭博自1993年追蹤市場以來盤中最高價，超過了2011年的紀錄高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白銀價格今年以來已上漲逾70%，令黃金創紀錄的漲幅相形見絀。美國財政風險、股市過熱且聯儲會獨立面臨威脅等因素引發投資者擔憂，他們也由此加大了對避險資產的追捧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，關鍵的倫敦市場上白銀供應短缺也支撐了價格，同時還大幅推高了借入該金屬的成本。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7edc7236-5e6c-3d02-94ec-d31de8d809ef-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Spot Silver Hits Highest in Decades on Haven Rally, Tight Market</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%81%BF%E9%9A%AA%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E9%81%87%E4%B8%8A%E7%B7%8A%E4%BF%8F%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8%E7%99%BD%E9%8A%80%E5%89%B5%E5%87%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-123441859.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-09 21:15:55",
